For pubsub in python
	twisted + wokkel
		Try to use PubSubClient.
		PubSubResource and PubSubService are for servers.
	PubSubClient
		Affero
		http://github.com/Warbo/pubsubclient
		http://pubsubclient.sourceforge.net/

Can use ejabber + idavoll (based on wokkel) as a pubsub server,
or use plain ejabberd 2.0.0+. I don't know if plain idavoll is possible.
* http://www.josephguhlin.com/blog/archives/2007/04/10/on-being-late-to-the-party-or-pubsub-jabber-and-pain/
* http://www.ejabberd.im/ejabberd-2.0.0

